I didn’t think I’d look forward to wearing sunscreen every day… until this one.
The Cell Fusion C Laser Sunscreen 100 SPF 50+/PA+++ is one of those formulas that makes your skin feel safe and spoiled at the same time.
It’s got that weightless, no-white-cast texture that melts in like skincare and because it’s packed with ingredients like Niacinamide + Zinc Oxide, it’s more than just sun protection. It’s calming, helps with redness, and gives your skin that subtle, healthy sheen (read: not greasy, just glowy ✨).
If your skin’s sensitive, post-treatment, or just easily overwhelmed this is the one.⁣
